title: 40 years since NASA's Challenger space shuttle disaster killed seven astronauts
description: It's been 40 years since NASA's Challenger disaster. The space shuttle exploded 73 seconds after take-off, killing all seven astronauts on board including teacher Christa McAuliffe.
